Leverage = use something effectively
We should leverage data for better decisions.
Optimize = improve efficiency
We need to optimize this process.
Streamline = make simpler & faster
Let’s streamline the workflow.
Escalate = move to higher authority
I will escalate this issue to management.
Mitigate = reduce risk/problem
We need to mitigate potential risks.
Facilitate = make easier
This tool will facilitate communication.
Implement = put into action
We will implement the new strategy.
Analyze = study carefully
Let’s analyze the results.
Coordinate = work together smoothly
Please coordinate with the team.
Execute = carry out a plan
We need to execute this properly.
